(753, 'the_gedcom_file', 'The GEDCOM file format is the worldwide standard\r\n              format for storing genealogical information. With this format, you\r\n              will be able to import your tree into other genealogical software,\r\n              like desktop family tree creators and public genealogical databases.', 'english', 'utf-8'),
